---
title: Herby Shrimp Pie with Sweet Peas
description: Time for a coastal twist on the classic pot pie! Tonight's juicy shrimp, sweet pea and herb pie is topped with layers of buttery puff pastry. Break the crust on this creamy, dreamy dinner and dig in!
